sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Client
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant BG as Background task
  participant Pipe as Ingestion pipeline
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  Client->>API: POST /documents multipart
  API->>DB: INSERT document + ingestion_job
  API-->>Client: document_id job_id
  API->>BG: schedule process_ingestion_job
  BG->>Pipe: run_ingestion
  Pipe->>DB: parse chunk embed UPDATE chunks
  Pipe->>DB: job status ready or error
  Client->>API: GET /documents/id/ingestion
  API-->>Client: status progress
